      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the general mood. I want to get more specific with the character dynamics though. For this particular scene, I want to emphasize the tension between the generations. Like, could you describe how the younger kids might act compared to the older adults? Specifically, maybe mention if there's any friction around things like how they're being raised or even how they interact with their culture/traditions? I want to make sure I'm hitting those realistic cultural tropes for the script.",
